name: COMPUTER SCIENCE ENRICHMENT CLUB (CSEC)
content: The Computer Science Enrichment Club is a student-run group that focuses on helping students with a passion for Computer Science take the next steps in their professional careers.

name: WOMEN IN COMPUTER SCIENCE, STATISTICS AND MATHEMATICS (WiCSM)
content: WiCSM creates communal, academic, and skillful events to create safe place for students to come together & socialize through events. Our main goal is to encourage more women to pursue a degree in Computer Science, Statistics & Mathematics.
